<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Sarah_Siddons_as_Euphrasia_in_The_Grecian_Daughter,_1782.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
<a href="/wiki/Sarah_Siddons" title="Sarah Siddons">Sarah Siddons</a> as <a href="/wiki/Euphrasia" title="Euphrasia">Euphrasia</a> in a 1782 production of <a href="/wiki/Arthur_Murphy" title="Arthur Murphy">Murphy's</a> tragedy <i>The Grecian Daughter</i>.</div>
